SIMPLE: uncontrollable
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncontrollable
<hw>Un`con*trol"la*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Incapable of being controlled; ungovernable; irresistible; <as>as,
an <ex>uncontrollable</ex> temper; <ex>uncontrollable</ex>
events</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Indisputable; irrefragable; <as>as, an
<ex>uncontrollable</ex> maxim; an <ex>uncontrollable</ex>
title</as>.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Un`con*trol"la*ble*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos> --
<wf>Un`con*trol"la*bly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncontroversory</ent>⟦br⟧
